{"tid":2250784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國將最快在明年一月將會試行注射武肺病毒予健康人士身上","createTime":"2020-10-20T10:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T16:38:17.000Z","uid":38861,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"be7fa4264743255fcb51c65a5e1ccd2f9e67d740","tid":2250784,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"疫苗臨床測試能否得出確定性的結果，將取決於感染武肺的真正人數。<br />\n<br />\n根據目前標準，當疫苗能夠阻擋50%受感染人士出現武肺徵狀的話，FDA便會批准該疫苗公開進入市場。<br />\n<br />\n為加快疫苗試驗進度，英國政府在10月20日公佈，將給予設於愛爾蘭首都都柏林名為OpenOrphan的公司13million美金，最快在明年1月實踐將武肺病毒注射在測試者身上、然後再注射各種疫苗，觀察其反應及疫苗效率。<br />\n<br />\n首次試驗暫時推算會召集30-50名18-30歲的健康人士，其間留院密切觀察，而每位測試者將獲4000英磅，且某部份人士注射病毒後將會只獲得安慰劑而非疫苗 。<br />\n<br />\n武肺病毒注射測試註冊網站：<a href=\"https://ukcovidchallenge.com/covid-19-volunteer-trials/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fukcovidchallenge.com%2Fcovid-19-volunteer-trials%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=43ca009a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ukcovidchallenge.com/covid-19-volunteer-trials/</a><br />\n<br />\n文章Source:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-02821-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-020-02821-4&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=8c8f3aa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-02821-4</a>"},{"pid":"2f6707a947b7c33b99369386a45cb4bdaa4a214c","tid":2250784,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"4000 英磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae488235902bd6811218f2d3b921fa8778914853","tid":2250784,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f6707a947b7c33b99369386a45cb4bdaa4a214c","tid":2250784,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"4000 英磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,